snippet.title: Serial Cleaners Reveal Teaser
snippet.description:
Wishlist the game on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1337920/Serial_Cleaners/
Serial Cleaners is coming to PC, consoles and possibly next-gens on 2021.
Serial Cleaners is a single-player stealth action crime story in which you alternate between playing four eccentric mob cleaners taking on the bloodiest jobs the carefree 1990s had to offer. If you remember the nineties differently, their dirty work is the reason why. 
Follow the game on : https://www.facebook.com/drawdistancedev/ and https://www.facebook.com/serialcleanerofficial/
https://twitter.com/DrawDistanceDev
